OVERVIEW
--------

Konfa.pm is a configuration encapsulator that normalises access to config values
throughout an application. It implements a few mechanisms to avoid mistakes when
dealing with configuration in a large, long lived application.

DOCUMENTATION
-------------

The following documentation is available:

* POD in perldoc format (type "perldoc Konfa" on the command line.)

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------

Currently, this module is not on CPAN, so installation is manual:


  git clone git@github.com:avidity/konfa-perl
  cd konfa-perl
  perl Build.pl
  ./Build installdeps
  ./Build test
  ./Build install

